  "text": "The second comment is that Eq. (12) is not only the unifying description of the known parity-violating terms L CS , L PV1 , and L PV2 , but also the low-energy effective description of generic parity-violating GWs. Indeed, the same quadratic action was derived from the viewpoint of the effective field theory in [CITATION_1] . In light of this viewpoint, one may, for example, further add terms like",
